uphold by His providence.51 In order to bring redemption, God established covenants52 
which revealed His grace to sinful people.53 In the covenant with Abraham, God bound 
Himself to His people Israel, promising to deliver them from bondage to sin and Satan 
and to bless all the nations through them.54 
